                    <h3>Overview</h3>
                    <p>The Madison College Mail Center and Shipping/Recieving bay is
                    where all the mail is received, sorted, and shipped.</p>

                </div>
                <div id="menu1" class="tab-pane fade">
                    <h3>Services</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Folding/Inserting</li>
                        <li>Metering</li>
                        <li>Outbound Packages</li>
                        <li>Inkjetting/Mailpiece Design</li>
                        <li>Address Correction/Hygiene</li>
                        <li>Assign/Manage Mailboxes</li>
                        <li>Insured/Certified Mail</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div id="menu2" class="tab-pane fade">
                    <h3>Deliveries and Pick Up Times</h3>
                    <h5>Monday - Friday</h5>
                    <ul>
                        <li>9:00am - Mail is recieved and sorted at the mail center</li>
                        <li>9:30am - Mail is delivered to Foundation Building, South Madison Campus, and West Madison Campus</li>
                        <li>10:00am - Mail is delivered to departments within Truax Main Campus Building</li>
                        <li>11:30am - Mail is delivered to Health Building, Human Protective Services Building, Commercial Ave Campus,
                            Downtown Campus, and Foundation Building</li>
                        <li>1:00pm - Mail is delivered to departments within Truax Main Campus Building</li>
                        <li>3:30pm - Outgoing USPS mail is picked up from the mail center.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
